{"kanda":6,"sarga":87,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"एवमुक्त्वातुसौमित्रिंजातहर्षोविभीषणः ।धनुष्पाणिंनमादायत्वरमाणोजगामसः","trans":"Vibheeshana, having spoken that way, Saumithri was satisfied. Wielding a bow Saumithri went quickly with Vibheeshana.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"सौमित्रिम्","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"जातहर्षः","m":"satisfied"},{"d":"धनुष्पाणिम्","m":"wielding bow"},{"d":"न","m":"him"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"taking"},{"d":"जगाम","m":"went"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"अविदूरंततोगत्वाप्रविश्यतुमहद्वनम् ।दर्शमामासतत्कर्मलक्ष्मणातविभीषणः","trans":"Thereafter Vibheeshana followed Lakshmana for a small distance to the forest and showed him What to do.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"अविदूरम्","m":"little distance"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"went"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"वनम्","m":"forest"},{"d":"प्रविश्य","m":"entered"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणाय","m":"with Lakshmana"},{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"What to do"},{"d":"दर्शयामास","m":"showed"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"नीलजीमूतसङ्काशंन्यग्रोधंभीमदर्शनम् ।तेजस्वीरावणभ्रातालक्ष्मणायन्यवेदयत्","trans":"Vibheeshana, the brilliant brother of Ravana, showed Lakshmana a banyan tree resembling a dark cloud, frightening to look at.","words":[{"d":"तेजस्वी","m":"brilliant"},{"d":"रावणभ्राता","m":"Ravana's brother"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणाय","m":"to Lakshmana"},{"d":"नीलजीमूतसङ्काशम्","m":"resembling dark clouds"},{"d":"भीमदर्शनम्","m":"frightening to look"},{"d":"न्यग्रोधम्","m":"a banyan tree"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणायन्यवेदयत्","m":"showed to Lakshmana"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"इहोपहारंभूतानांबलवान्रावणात्मजः ।उपहृत्यततःपश्चात्सङ्ग्राममभिवर्तते","trans":"\"Mighty son of Ravana having offered oblations for all beings he comes to the battlefield. (Said Vibheeshana)\"","words":[{"d":"बलवान्","m":"mighty"},{"d":"रावणात्मजः","m":"Ravana's son"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"भूतानाम्","m":"for all beings"},{"d":"उपहारम्","m":"oblations"},{"d":"उपहृत्य","m":"having offered"},{"d":"पश्