बलवान्","m":"endowed with mighty prowess"},{"d":"कवची","m":"shield"},{"d":"खङ्गी","m":"sword"},{"d":"सःइन्द्रजित्","m":"that Indrajith"},{"d":"अग्निवर्णेन","m":"glowing like gold"},{"d":"रथेन","m":"in the chariot"},{"d":"प्रत्यदृश्यत","m":"appeared"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"तमुवाचमहातेजाःपौलस्त्यमपराजितम् ।समह्वयेत्वांसमरेसम्यग्युद्धंप्रयच्छमे","trans":"Lakshmana of extraordinary energy, spoke to Indrajith of the Paulastya clan,\" I challenge you to fight in battle directly. Fight with me.\"","words":[{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly energetic"},{"d":"अपराजितम्","m":"who has never been defeated"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"पौलस्त्यम्","m":"of Paulastya clan"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"said"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"to him"},{"d":"समरे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"समाह्वये","m":"challenging you"},{"d":"सम्यक्","m":"encounter"},{"d":"मे","m":"me"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"fight"},{"d":"प्रयच्छ","m":"directly"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"एवमुक्तोमहातेजामनस्वीरावणात्मजः ।अब्रवीत्परुषंवाक्यंतत्रदृष्टवाविभीषणम्","trans":"Having spoken that way, highly energetic and strong minded Indrajith seeing Vibheeshana spoke to him harshly as follows.","words":[{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly energetic"},{"d":"मनस्वी","m":"minded"},{"d":"रावणात्मजः","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"to Vibheeshana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"परुषम्","m":"harsh"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoken"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"इहत्वंजातसम्वृद्धःसाक्षाद्भ्रातापितुर्मम ।कथंद्रुह्यसिपुत्रस्यपितृव्योममराक्षस","trans":"\"O Rakshasa! You are born here and brought up by my father. You are my father'sbrother also. How can you be hostile to your son?\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षस","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"पितुः","m":"father"},{"d":"साक्षात्","m":"real"},{"d":"भ्राता","m":"brother"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"पितृव्यः","m":"father too"},{"d":"पुत्रस्यकथम्","m":"with son how"},{"d":"द्रुह्यसि","m":"hostile"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"न ज्ञातित्वं न सौहार्धं न जातिस्तवदुर्मते ।प्रमाणं न च सौदर्यं न धर्मोधर्मदूषण","trans":"\"Evil minded Vibheeshana! You are vitiating righteousness, have no value to your race, no affection to your clan, no brotherly feeling and have no righteousness.\"","words":[{"d":"दुर्मते","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"धर्मदूषण","m":"vitiating righteousness"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"ज्ञातित्वम्","m":"race"},{"d":"न प्रमाणम्","m":"not valuing"},{"d":"सौहार्दम्","m":"affection"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"जातिः","m":"clan"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"सौदर्यम्","m":"brotherly feeling"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"धर्मः","m":"righteousness"},{"d":"न","m":"not"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"शोच्यस्त्वमसिदुर्बुद्धेनिन्दनीयश्चसाधुभिः ।यस्त्वंस्वजनमुत्सृज्यपरभृत्यत्वमागतः","trans":"\"You are evil minded, think. You are pitiable and to be blamed for you have abandoned your own people and sought the enemy's protection.\"","words":[{"d":"दुर्बुद्धे","m":"evil minded"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"शोच्यः","m":"think"},{"d":"साधुभिः","m":"pitiable"},{"d":"निन्दनीयश्च","m":"blamed"},{"d":"असि","m":"also"},{"d":"यःत्वम्","m":"your"},{"d":"स्वजनम्","m":"your own people"},{"d":"उत्सृज्य","m":"sought"},{"d":"परभृत्यत्वम्","m":"enemy's protection"},{"d":"आगतः","m":"came"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"नैतछचिथिलयाबुद्ध्यात्वंवेसतिमहदन्तरम् ।क्व च स्वजनसम्वासःक्व च नीचपराश्रयः","trans":"\"You do not seem to have an understanding of the difference between living with one's own people and seeking refuge from strangers. Your intellect has slackened you are not knowing.\"","words":[{"d":"स्वजनसम्वासः","m":"living with own people"},{"d":"क्व च","m":"is it that"},{"d":"नीचपराश्रयः","m":"seeking refuge from strangers"},{"d":"क्वच","m":"is it that"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"this"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"अन्तरम्","m":"understanding"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"शिथिलयता","m":"slackened"},{"d":"बुद्ध्या","m":"intellect"},{"d":"न वेसति","m":"not knowing"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"गुणवान्वापरजनःस्वजनोनिर्गुणोऽपिवा ।निर्गुणःस्वजनःश्रेयान् यःपरःपरएवसः","trans":"\"Even if others are virtuous and your own people are not virtuous also one should seek the refuge of one's own people. Strangers are always strangers.\"","words":[{"d":"परजनः","m":"others"},{"d":"गुणवान्वा","m":"virtuous"},{"d":"स्वजनः","m":"own people"},{"d":"निर्गुणोपिवा","m":"not virtuous also"},{"d":"निर्गुणः","m":"not virtuous"},{"d":"स्वजनः","m":"own people"},{"d":"श्रेयान्","m":"welfare"},{"d":"यः","m":"that which"},{"d":"परः","m":"others"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"परएवहि","m":"even if he"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"यसस्स्वपक्षंपरित्यज्यपरपक्षंनिषेवते ।स स्वपक्षेक्ष्यंप्राप्तेपश्चास्त्तैरेवहन्यते","trans":"\"He who renounces his own kind and seeks refuge from others, will be destroyed by others whose refuge he sought when his own people are destroyed.\"","words":[{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"स्वपक्षम्","m":"own side"},{"d":"परित्यज्य","m":"renouncing"},{"d":"परपक्षम्","m":"others side"},{"d":"निषेवते","m":"seeks refuge"},{"d":"स्वपक्षे","m":"own side"},{"d":"क्ष्यम्","m":"destruction"},{"d":"प्राप्ते","m":"happens"},{"d":"पश्चात्","m":"whose refuge was sought"},{"d":"तैरेव","m":"by them only"},{"d":"हन्यते","m":"destroyed"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"निरनुक्रोशताचेयंयादृशीतेनिशाचर ।स्वजनेनत्वयाशक्यंपौरुषंरावणानुज","trans":"\"O Ravana's brother! You have shown ruthlessness this way. O night ranger! Only you could exhibit this kind of manliness.\"","words":[{"d":"रावणानुज","m":"Ravana's brother"},{"d":"निशाचर","m":"night ranger"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"इयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"यादृशी","m":"way"},{"d":"निरनुक्रोशता","m":"ruthlessness"},{"d":"पौरुषम्","m":"manliness"},{"d":"स्वजनेन","m":"own people"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"शक्यम्","m":"is possible"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"इत्युक्तोभ्रातृपुत्रेणप्रत्युवाचविभीषणः ।अजानन्निवमछचीलंकिंराक्षसविकत्थसे","trans":"Indrajith having spoken like that, Vibheeshana replied,\" why do you speak like that as though you do not know my disposition?\"","words":[{"d":"भ्रातृपुत्रेण","m":"brother's son"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"प्रत्युवाच","m":"replied back"},{"d":"राक्षस","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"मछचीलम्","m":"my disposition"},{"d":"अजानन्निव","m":"as though you did not know"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"विकत्थसे","m":"speak like this"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"राक्षसेन्द्रसुतासाधोपारुष्यंत्यजगौरवात् ।कुलेयद्यप्यहंजातोरक्षसांक्रूरकर्मणाम् गुणोयःप्रथमोनृणंतन्मेशीलमराक्षसम् ।","trans":"\"Impious son of Rakshasa king! Though born in the Rakshasa clan I renounced cruel deeds and followed respectfully manliness as my primary quality. My nature is not like that of Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"असाधो","m":"impious"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रसुत","m":"son of Rakshasa king"},{"d":"गौरवात्","m":"respectfully"},{"d":"पारुष्यम्","m":"manliness"},{"d":"त्यज","m":"renounce"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"क्रूरकर्मणाम्","m":"cruel deeds"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"कुले","m":"clan"},{"d":"जातःयद्यपि","m":"though born"},{"d":"नृणाम्","m":"king"},{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"प्रथमः","m":"primary"},{"d":"गुणः","m":"quality"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"मे","m":"I"},{"d":"अराक्षसम्","m":"not Rakshasa like"},{"d":"शीलम्","m":"nature"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"न रमेदारुणेनाहं न चाधर्मेणवैरमे भ्रात्राविषशीलोऽपिकथंभ्रातानिरस्यते ।","trans":"\"I do not delight in cruel deeds, nor follow unrighteousness. Or else because of unfavourable disposition how can a brother be expelled by a brother?\"","words":[{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"दारुणेन","m":"cruel"},{"d":"न रमे","m":"not revel"},{"d":"अधर्मेण च","m":"unrighteousness"},{"d":"न रमेवै","m":"not follow"},{"d":"विषमशीलोऽपि","m":"of unfavourable disposition"},{"d":"भ्राता","m":"a brother"},{"d":"भ्रात्रा","m":"by a brother"},{"d":"कथम्","m":"how निरस्यते expelled"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"धर्मात्प्रच्युतशीलंहिपुरुषंपापनिश्चयम् त्यक्त्वासुखमवाप्नोतिहस्तादाशीविषंयथा ।","trans":"\"The association of one who has renounced righteousness and is of sinful deeds is left by a righteous man who undoubtedly attains happiness, is like shaking of a venomous serpent from the hand.\"","words":[{"d":"धर्मात्","m":"righteous"},{"d":"प्रच्युतशीलम्","m":"who has renounced"},{"d":"पापनिश्चयम्","m":"of sinful deeds"},{"d":"पुरुषम्","m":"man"},{"d":"हस्तात्","m":"from hand"},{"d":"आशीविषंयथा","m":"venomous serpent"},{"d":"त्यक्त्वा","m":"renouncing"},{"d":"सुखम्","m":"happiness"},{"d":"अवाप्नोति","m":"attains"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"परस्वहरणेयुक्तंपरदाराभिमर्शकम् त्याज्यमाहुर्दुरात्मानंवेश्मप्रज्वलितंयथा ।","trans":"\"Seizing the property of others, uniting with others wife, evil mindedness is said to be given up like getting out of a burning house.\"","words":[{"d":"परस्वहरणे","m":"seizing property of others"},{"d":"युक्तम्","m":"united"},{"d":"परदाराभिमर्शकम्","m":"with others wife"},{"d":"दुरात्मानम्","m":"evil mindedness"},{"d":"प्रज्वलितम्","m":"burning"},{"d":"वेश्मयथा","m":"like house"},{"d":"त्याज्यम्","m":"getting out"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"परस्वानां च हरणंपरदाराभिमर्शनम् सुहृदामतिशङ्का च त्रयोदोषाःक्षयावहाः ।","trans":"\"Stealing the wealth of others, possessing others wife, distrusting friends, these three faults will destroy a person.\"","words":[{"d":"परस्वानाम्","m":"others wealth"},{"d":"हरणम्","m":"stealing"},{"d":"परदाराभिमर्शनम्","m":"possessing others wife"},{"d":"सुहृदाम्","m":"friends"},{"d":"अतिशङ्का च","m":"distrusting"},{"d":"त्रयःदोषाः","m":"three faults"},{"d":"क्षयावहाः","m":"will destroy"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"महर्षीणांवधोघोरस्सर्वदेवैश्चविग्रहः अभिमानश्चदोषश्चवैरित्वंप्रतिकूलता ।एतेदोषाममभ्रातुर्जीवितैश्वर्यनाशनाः गुणान्प्रच्छादयामासुःपर्वतानिवतोयदाः ।","trans":"\"Dreadful killing of sages, haughtiness towards deities, irascibility, anger, animosity, refractorinessall these faults will put an end to one's life. These faults have obscured my brother's future just as rainy clouds veil the mountain.\"","words":[{"d":"महर्षीणाम्","m":"sages"},{"d":"घोरः","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"वधः","m":"killing"},{"d":"सर्वदेवैः","m":"all deities"},{"d":"विग्रहः च","m":"haughtiness"},{"d":"अभिमानश्च","m":"irascibility"},{"d":"रोषः च","m":"anger"},{"d":"वैरित्वं च","m":"animosity"},{"d":"प्रतिकूलता","m":"refractoriness"},{"d":"जीवितैश्वरनाशनाः","m":"put an end to one's life"},{"d":"एते","m":"all these"},{"d":"दोषाः","m":"faults"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"भ्रातुः","m":"brother's"},{"d":"गुणान्","m":"qualities"},{"d":"तोयदाः","m":"rainy clouds"},{"d":"पर्वतानिव","m":"mountains"},{"d":"प्रच्छादयामासुः","m":"put an end to future"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"महर्षीणांवधोघोरस्सर्वदेवैश्चविग्रहः अभिमानश्चदोषश्चवैरित्वंप्रतिकूलता ।एतेदोषाममभ्रातुर्जीवितैश्वर्यनाशनाः गुणान्प्रच्छादयामासुःपर्वतानिवतोयदाः ।","trans":"\"Dreadful killing of sages, haughtiness towards deities, irascibility, anger, animosity, refractorinessall these faults will put an end to one's life. These faults have obscured my brother's future just as rainy clouds veil the mountain.\"","words":[{"d":"महर्षीणाम्","m":"sages"},{"d":"घोरः","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"वधः","m":"killing"},{"d":"सर्वदेवैः","m":"all deities"},{"d":"विग्रहः च","m":"haughtiness"},{"d":"अभिमानश्च","m":"irascibility"},{"d":"रोषः च","m":"anger"},{"d":"वैरित्वं च","m":"animosity"},{"d":"प्रतिकूलता","m":"refractoriness"},{"d":"जीवितैश्वरनाशनाः","m":"put an end to one's life"},{"d":"एते","m":"all these"},{"d":"दोषाः","m":"faults"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"भ्रातुः","m":"brother's"},{"d":"गुणान्","m":"qualities"},{"d":"तोयदाः","m":"rainy clouds"},{"d":"पर्वतानिव","m":"mountains"},{"d":"प्रच्छादयामासुः","m":"put an end to future"}]},{"v":26,"dev":"दोषैरेतैःपरित्यक्तोमयाभ्रातापितातव नेयमस्तिपुरीलङ्का न च त्वं न च तेपिता ।","trans":"\"Because of these faults your father and my brother has been abandoned by me from this Lanka. This Lanka will not be there, nor your father and you too.\"","words":[{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"पिता","m":"father"},{"d":"भ्राता","m":"brother"},{"d":"एतैःदोषैः","m":"these faults"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"इयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"लङ्कापुरी","m":"Lanka city"},{"d":"न अस्ति","m":"not be there"},{"d":"त्वम् च","m":"you too"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"पिता च","m":"father"},{"d":"न","m":"not"}]},{"v":27,"dev":"अतिमाननी च बालश्चदुर्विनीतश्चराक्षस ।बद्धस्त्वंकालपाशेनब्रूहिमांयद्यदिच्छसि","trans":"\"O Rakshasa! You are mean, proud of might, immoral and bound by the noose of death. Whatever you wish to say you may say.\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षस","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"अतिमानी च","m":"mean"},{"d":"बालश्च","m":"proud of might"},{"d":"दुर्विनीतश्च","m":"immoral"},{"d":"कालपाशेन","m":"by noose of death"},{"d":"बद्धः","m":"bound"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"your"},{"d":"माम्","m":"my"},{"d":"यत् यत्","m":"Whatever"},{"d":"इच्छसि","m":"wish to say"},{"d":"ब्रूहि","m":"say"}]},{"v":28,"dev":"अद्यतेव्यसनंप्राप्तंकिंमांत्वामिहवक्ष्यसि ।प्रवेष्टुं न त्वयाशक्यंन्यग्रोधंराक्षसाधम","trans":"\"O Lowly Rakshasa! This worry has come to you today. Entering the banyan tree is not possible for you today.\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षसाधम","m":"lowly among Rakshasas"},{"d":"किं","m":"why"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"your"},{"d":"वक्ष्यसि","m":"to you"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"व्यसनम्","m":"worry"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"न्यग्रोधम्","m":"banyan tree"},{"d":"प्रवेष्टुम्","m":"entering"},{"d":"न शक्यम्","m":"not possible"}]},{"v":29,"dev":"धर्षयित्वा च काकुत्स्थं न शक्यंजीवितुंत्वया ।युध्यस्वनरदेवेनलक्ष्मणेनरणेसह हतस्त्वंदेवताकार्यंकरिष्यसियमक्षये ।","trans":"\"Clashing with Lakshmana of Kakuthsa clan is not possible for you. By waging war with Lakshmana, you will be killed and reaching the abode of the Lord of death. You will be doing tasks of deities of Devatas.\"","words":[{"d":"काकुत्स्थम्","m":"Kakuthsa"},{"d":"धर्षयित्वा","m":"clashing"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"जीवितुम्","m":"life"},{"d":"न शक्यम्","m":"not possible"},{"d":"रणए","m":"in combat"},{"d":"नरदेवेन","m":"god of retribution"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणेनसहस","m":"with Lakshmana"},{"d":"युध्यस्व","m":"waging war"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"हतः","m":"killed"},{"d":"यमक्षये","m":"abode of yama"},{"d":"देवताकार्यम्","m":"tasks of Devatas"},{"d":"करिष्यसि","m":"will be doing"}]}]}